:TITLE:
Initial Surveyor 
:CONTENT:
All participants in the Incident Command System(ICS) are first Initial Surveyors.  
As you leave for the Incident Command Center or the Division Assembly Point first check 
your close neighbors for any emergency situations.
On you way to join the ICS neighborhood group,
from the sidewalk, look for any damages, injuries, dangerous situations, or an all-clear signal.
Record each of your observations on a Damage Assessment Form.
:LIST:
